        "\n",
        "## To find complete solution to Ax=b\n",
        "\n",
        "[To find complete solution to Ax=b](../appendices/8.md#to-find-complete-solution-to-axb)\n",
        "\n",
        "### $x_{particular}$\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Set all free variables to zero\n",
        "2. Solve Ax=b for pivot variables"
      ],
      "id": "fcab5cd0"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "import sympy as sp\n",
        "from IPython.display import display, Math, Markdown\n",
        "\n",
        "# 构造增广矩阵 [A|b]\n",
        "aug = sp.Matrix([\n",
        "    [1, 2, 1],\n",
        "    [0, 2, 3],\n",
        "])\n",
        "\n",
        "# 求行最简形，返回 (rref矩阵, 主元列下标)\n",
        "rref_mat, pivot = aug.rref()\n",
        "display(Markdown(\"增广矩阵行最简形：\"), rref_mat)\n",
        "display(Markdown(f\"最后一列就是方程的解：${sp.latex(rref_mat[:, -1])}$\"))\n",
        "display(Markdown(\"主元列：\"), pivot)"
      ],
